@vickiespencer How awful for them to wait a month! I was screaming on morphine for four agonizing days before they took the stone out. The morphine did nothing. I’m not happy they waited four days. It was three days before a urologist even came to see me.
I have had only 1 soda since then, in the last three years, as I read that can cause them, and try to drink as much water every day as possible. I aim for a liter.
I feel so bad for your husband! I wonder why they would allow him to suffer for a month like that. He has my complete sympathy. I never knew pain could be that bad.
